text: Deep Springs may refer to: *Deep Springs, California, unincorporated community in Inyo County *Deep Springs College, nontraditional two-year institution located in Deep Springs Valley *Deep Springs International, sponsor of the Gayden Dlo point of use water treatment program *Deep Springs Plantation, a mansion in Stoneville, North Carolina *Deep Springs Valley, valley in the Inyo-White mountain range of California
title: Deep Springs
